thread.title: Carissa Mean

author: Carissa Mean
title: Carissa Mean
text: This is a great organization to be apart of. They help Their members with career searches, with searching for cheaper textbooks, and offer many discounts. They also provide many networking opportunities. I went with a large group from the organization on a trip to Washington DC and was extremely happy with the amount of activities that were packed into the trip. This trip was fun, informative, and allowed me to meet many people from all over the country. I would definitely do this again!
